*************TestNG Class02*************

Установить плагин XML-->
--> кликнуть правой кнопкой по проекту
--> выбрать create XML PROJECT
--> кликнуть OK
--> перезапустить проект (reload)
--> зайти в появившийся файл testing.xml
--> code -> reformat code


TestNG XML:
gives u control over the execution of your whole project!!!
дает вам контроль над выполнением всего вашего проекта!!!

<suite>
     <test>
            <classes>
                <class>
                    <method>
                    </method>
                <class>
            </classes>
         <packages>

        </packages>
    </test>
</suite>

@BeforeClass:
this is annotation is used to execute the method only once before the execution of the class.

@AfterClass:
this is annotation is used to execute the method only once after the execution of the class.

@BeforeTest:
this is annotation is used to execute the method only once before the execution of the test.

@AfterTest:
this is annotation is used to execute the method only once after the execution of the test.

whenever we run by groups
the @beforeMethod and @AfterMethods do not run
because they are not under the tag of groups

When we run by method name
@before method and @after method